farsight: farsight (Farsight Communications Framework)
farsight:
farsight: Farsight is an effort to create a framework to deal with all known 
farsight: audio/video conferencing protocols for use by applications such as 
farsight: instant messaging. These applications are able to use Farsight for 
farsight: all their Audio/Video conferencing needs without having to worry 
farsight: about any of the lower level streaming and NAT traversal issues.  
farsight:
farsight: Farsight forms an integral part of the Telepathy framework.
